</nav>

<div class="container-fluid px-5">
  <div class="text-center mb-4">
    <h2 class="section-title">My Certifications</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center">

    <!-- AWS Technical Essentials -->
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex">
      <div class="achievement-card shadow-sm p-3 h-100 border border-primary">
        <iframe src="/certs/aws.pdf" class="cert-iframe mb-3"></iframe>
        <h5 class="card-title">AWS Technical Essentials</h5>
        <strong>Description:</strong>
        <p class="card-text">Attained foundational knowledge of AWS services and cloud computing concepts.</p>
        <strong>What I Learned:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>Core AWS services like EC2, S3, RDS and what they are used for</li>
          <li>Basic cloud architecture principles</li>
          <li>Security and compliance basics in cloud environments</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-blue mt-2" href="/certs/aws.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Full PDF</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AWS Cloud Practitioner -->
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex">
      <div class="achievement-card shadow-sm p-3 h-100 border border-primary">
        <iframe src="/certs/cloud-practitioner.pdf" class="cert-iframe mb-3"></iframe>
        <h5 class="card-title">AWS Cloud Practitioner</h5>
        <strong>Description:</strong>
        <p class="card-text">Officially certified as an AWS Cloud Practitioner, applying foundational cloud concepts and core services in AWS like Lambda, DynamoDB, and CloudFront.</p>
        <strong>What I Learned:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>Understanding use cases and definitions of AWS services like Lambda, DynamoDB, and CloudFront</li>
          <li>Basic foundational cloud concepts such as scalability, elasticity, and high availability</li>
          <li>Security and compliance basics in cloud environments</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-blue mt-2" href="/certs/cloud-practitioner.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Full PDF</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Understanding LLMs -->
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex">
      <div class="achievement-card shadow-sm p-3 h-100 border border-primary">
        <iframe src="/certs/llms.pdf" class="cert-iframe mb-3"></iframe>
        <h5 class="card-title">Understanding LLMs</h5>
        <strong>Description:</strong>
        <p class="card-text">Learned about large language models and gained insights into AI concepts like prompting and differences between model versions.</p>
        <strong>What I Learned:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>Understanding of what large language models are and how they work</li>
          <li>Insights into AI concepts like prompting and the differences between model versions</li>
          <li>Gained hands-on experience with prompt engineering techniques</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-blue mt-2" href="/certs/llms.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Full PDF</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Youth Action Forum -->
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex">
      <div class="achievement-card shadow-sm p-3 h-100 border border-primary">
        <iframe src="/certs/youth action forum.pdf" class="cert-iframe mb-3"></iframe>
        <h5 class="card-title">Youth Action Forum</h5>
        <strong>Description:</strong>
        <p class="card-text">Participated in the Tech For Good theme in Youth Action Forum, brainstorming ideas on how youths can use technology for social good.</p>
        <strong>What I Learned:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>Gained insights on how technology can be used for social good</li>
          <li>Brainstormed and collaborated with peers to build solutions with LEGO pieces</li>
          <li>Enhanced communication and teamwork skills through group discussions and presentations</li>
          <li>Developed innovation and creative problem-solving skills</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-blue mt-2" href="/certs/youth action forum.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Full PDF</a>
        <a class="btn btn-blue mt-2" href="/images/youth_action_forumps.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View Problem Statement</a>
      </div>
    </div>
       

  </div>
